description: Product description Say hello to the animals down on the farm with Jaques of London’s Wooden Farm Animal Puzzle—perfect for toddlers aged 1+. This charming Montessori-inspired set includes a square wooden puzzle board and 12 chunky animal pieces, from pigs and cows to chickens and sheep. Each animal fits its matching outline and includes its name to help with early recognition. Crafted using sustainable materials and painted with child-safe, water-based colours, it’s a safe, sturdy way to encourage early development. Packaged in signature Jaques ribbon-tied gift boxing, this puzzle is the perfect introduction to animals, learning, and imaginative play—farmyard fun at its finest! Safety Warning Not Suitable for children under 12 months. Due to the size and shape of certain components
